- [ ] All storage adapters have file system integration tests
- [ ] Concurrent access tested with 10+ parallel operations
- [ ] Index corruption recovery tested
- [ ] Performance benchmarks: <5s for 1000 items
- [ ] Temp directories cleaned up after tests

